				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Today in Small Business: Yelp Video</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Gene Marks			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-07-29T17:13:56+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">July 29, 2014 1:13 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">July 29, 2014 1:13 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/07/29/today-in-small-business-yelp-video/" data-title="Today in Small Business: Yelp Video" data-description="Ten things American have stopped buying. Why dollar stores are struggling. And why the economy grows faster under Democratic presidents.">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>The Economy</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Economists are predicting that <a href="//www.reuters.com/article/2014/07/28/us-usa-economy-gdp-idUSKBN0FX1FA20140728?f">economic growth rebounded</a> in the second quarter and will continue to gather momentum.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Home-price growth <a href="//online.wsj.com/articles/home-price-growth-slows-sharply-case-shiller-says-1406638837">slowed sharply</a> and pending home sales <a href="//www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-pending-home-sales-20140728-story.html">unexpectedly fell in June</a>.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ <a href="//news.yahoo.com/u-services-sector-activity-accelerates-july-markit-135330754--business.html">Service sector activity</a> accelerated and Texas <a href="//econintersect.com/b2evolution/blog1.php/2014/07/28/july-2014-texas-manufacturing-survey-rate-of-growth-improves">manufacturing improved</a> in July.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Ford is <a href="//www.foxbusiness.com/markets/2014/07/28/ford-raising-prices-on-new-aluminum-sided-f-150/">raising prices</a> on a truck thatâs popular with business owners.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Start-Up</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A start-up <a href="//www.marketplace.org/topics/tech/start-incubator-veterans#.U9eTWi6iUQc.twitter">incubator for veterans</a> is opening in Chicago.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A mom starts a business <a href="//www.currentzionsville.com/2014/07/28/school-mom-business-owner-kids-eat/">to help children</a> eat better. <span id="more-87584"></span></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Online</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Yelp <a href="//www.webpronews.com/yelp-launches-video-upload-feature-is-your-business-ready-2014-07">introduces</a> a feature that will allow its users to take video inside your business and post them.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ OKCupid <a href="//www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/07/28/its-not-just-facebook-okcupid-admits-to-experimenting-with-user-compatability-data/">admits experimenting</a> with user data.</p>
