<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A study asks why the economy grows <a href="//www.vox.com/2014/7/29/5945583/the-us-economy-grows-faster-under-democratic-presidents-is-that-just">faster under Democratic presidents</a>.</p>
