<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A company has met its crowdfunding goal to manufacture a projector that <a href="https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/touchpico-turn-any-surface-into-a-touch-screen">turns any surface</a> into a touch screen.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The goal of this <a href="//recode.net/2014/07/28/game-changing-grilled-cheese-tech-2/">new delivery box</a> is to take a grilled cheese sandwich to the next level.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Opportunities</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here are 10 things Americans <a href="//time.com/money/3030959/guns-gum-soda-cereal-gluten-sales-drop/">have stopped</a> buying.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Apple is looking to <a href="//blogs.wsj.com/digits/2014/07/28/apple-looks-to-more-content-acquisitions/?">acquire companies</a> providing content.</p>
